me":"2020-10-31T11:30:10.000Z","msg":"17<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:31:49.000Z","msg":"屌，好快好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:34:53.000Z","msg":"最驚係有後遺症 有啲friend話之後會慣性拗柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:44:56.000Z","msg":"邊有呢d野呀，唔濕凍水，定返腳個形就無事。<br />\n<br />\n你睇鐵打要睇下個鐵打佬有無料到，同埋佢d藥用料足唔足。<br />\n<br />\n試過有次整到手，個客介紹我去上水睇佢個frd,  睇左2次係個師父老婆同仔幫我整，覺得無咩料到。第3次個師父自己幫我卒，卒完隻手順返8成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本頭2次就係昆水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb21887753eec3a0cf8d3d7c77b1fb2bcb24c3bf","tid":2265241,"uid":69975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:46:16.000Z","msg":"要睇下你傷勢同個師傅識唔識<br />\n單純拉傷韌帶嘅最緊要係消腫<br />\n同唔好比啲瘀血積住<br />\n<br />\n有啲時候拗到會有少少移位<br />\n過後會可以好似啪手指咁間唔中啪到聲<br />\n咁就要拉返正個臼位<br />\n部分物理治療（手法治療）同跌打會做到<br />\n睇你搵個個識唔識<br />\n（其實註冊中醫都要上堂學西醫理論唔代表唔識<br />\n係某啲醫館掛個醫師名搵個阿姐整帖藥幫你痴就算）<br />\n<br />\n至於慣性拗係傷完冇強化返周邊肌肉<br />\n同睇咩關係唔大係講自己努力<br />\n<br />\n利申踢波拗慣哂"},{"pid":"9448a8e3e8863f6245694b79a113a633e1a9c241","tid":2265241,"uid":259544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d31f0929307f5f522e9552f48610c191627dc76","tid":2265241,"uid":256796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2157876cc3f1732b7cc20d3a5e92689e789b650","tid":2265241,"uid":258999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff4e61716e17b6383987520498ad935a6e16d40a","tid":2265241,"uid":256796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:30:10.000Z","msg":"17<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:31:49.000Z","msg":"屌，好快好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:34:53.000Z","msg":"最驚係有後遺症 有啲friend話之後會慣性拗柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:48:21.000Z","msg":"一定會 <br />\n<br />\n由細拗到大 細個試過坐完一企起身都拗柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次以為好嚴重 都去照x光 但次次都係骨冇事 腫到隻雞蛋咁大<br />\n<br />\n睇跌打有d會卒 痛到仆街 話要率散d瘀血 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔覺會快d好<br />\n<br />\n之後跌打都廢事睇 頭一日用冰敷 之後幾日熱敷 加用d喜療妥自己查/敷過夜 自己會好<br />\n<br />\n宜家腳踝會大左一舊 好似話係拗得多 韌帶生大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e29ca6b375ff2ea0bfc1e598a03e41aad346347b","tid":2265241,"uid":165809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f392ea34d63896427f7d996f0f4b66ee724e746","tid":2265241,"uid":256796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"062c6daa9983ea065e1a7a9c20bd6dc33267086b","tid":2265241,"uid":185539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T10:34:01.000Z","msg":"唔痛就唔睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:24:10.000Z","msg":"就係痛...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:51:58.000Z","msg":"你照下有冇斷骨先好d"},{"pid":"d737c6c1043bdd1781a654372c8a1dc804659314","tid":2265241,"uid":15617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8667850d315f23ab801bbae009904d842d742b8d","tid":2265241,"uid":256796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T09:27:58.000Z","msg":"如題 其實有冇需要長睇 直至好返？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定還是有其他更好方法？<br />\n<br />\n今日睇咗第一次 見佢都係幫我捽藥油 同埋敷嘢<br />\n<br />\n有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T12:00:14.000Z","msg":"藥房買罐701,好過睇鐵打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968d89dd72021776d41f64ccd18bbdcb568f66dd","tid":2265241,"uid":135354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T12:01:25.000Z","msg":"拗過一次 睇咗幾次鐵打 <br />\n個師傅每次都幫我拉隻腳 唔係係拉返正個骹定點 痛到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過之後冇再拗過"},{"pid":"084989443f81edda0eb5437c2c2ba7b91226170a","tid":2265241,"uid":343977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T12:07:58.000Z","msg":"十幾年前右腳睇過跌打<br />\n比佢搞果陣痛到暈左<br />\n佢話唔收錢但唔再搞<br />\n然後再無幫襯過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上年左腳又仆街<br />\n成隻腳成個golf ball咁<br />\n但物理治療一個月行得翻山<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3c4e1a7f60899719d25241ca9be2da53bcb9fb2","tid":2265241,"uid":211894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T12:08:35.000Z","msg":"今年3月拗過<br />\n拗完腫到行唔到<br />\n單腳慢慢行<br />\n頭一個星期都係病假<br />\n睇急症都係比消炎藥<br />\n頭一個月keep住每星期覆診<br />\n初頭浸冰水<br />\n後期暖水<br />\n搽殺龍巴斯<br />\n到6月尾先正常跑得返步"},{"pid":"006681475e0236553c45f07766ff54fdf9241e32","tid":2265241,"uid":17904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T12:21:43.000Z","msg":"第幾日咬，頭4-5日都唔好睇，愈睇愈衰話你知，除左敷冰無野可以做，2-3個鐘敷一次快d去腫。btw咬得勁唔勁，咬果陣有無聲，有就要去醫院照，好有可能斷左野。<br />\n利伸：兩年前咬柴咬到斷左2條韌帶+骨裂"}]}